/span><o:page></o:page></p>\n  <p style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:等线;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;font-variant:normal;text-transform:none;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/7bb56000-56d4-4e42-61b1-929d37485f00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5034843205574913\" data-w=\"574\" style=\"width:553.739990234375px;height:278.79998779296875px;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/7bb56000-56d4-4e42-61b1-929d37485f00/public\"></span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;font-variant:normal;text-transform:none;mso-font-kerning:0.0pt;\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;font-variant:normal;text-transform:none;mso-font-kerning:0.0pt;\"><o:p>\n     <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;</span>\n    </o:p></span></p>\n  <p style=\"\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;font-variant:normal;text-transform:none;mso-font-kerning:0.0pt;font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">6.交流平台</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;font-variant:normal;text-transform:none;mso-font-kerning:0.0pt;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果您有任何意见、评论以及建议欢迎加入教材交流QQ群（群号：1036887023）。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-variant: normal;text-transform: none;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/377b9061-68d5-47c1-e7a3-c32a60746f00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.2987012987012987\" dat